---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact | Baksuls Blog" noindex={true}>
  <article class="static-page contact-page">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Have a question, suggestion, or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you!
      Use the information below to get in touch.
    </p>

    <section class="contact-info">
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

      <div class="contact-method">
        <h3>Email</h3>
        <p>
          For general inquiries, feedback, or collaboration opportunities, send us an email.
          We'll get back to you as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <p class="contact-detail">
          <a href="mailto:leolee.baksuls@gmail.com">leolee.baksuls@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Can I suggest a topic for an article?</h3>
        <p>
          Absolutely! We're always looking for new ideas. If there's something about Korea
          you'd like us to cover, send us an email with your suggestion.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>I found an error in one of your articles.</h3>
        <p>
          Thank you for helping us maintain accuracy! Please email us with the article link
          and the correction, and we'll review it promptly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Do you accept guest posts?</h3>
        <p>
          We occasionally feature guest content from writers with unique perspectives on Korea.
          If you're interested, send us a brief pitch with your topic idea and writing samples.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3>Interested in advertising or partnerships?</h3>
        <p>
          For business inquiries, sponsorships, or collaboration proposals, please reach out
          via email with details about your proposal.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="response-time">
      <h2>Response Time</h2>
      <p>
        We typically respond to emails within 1-3 business days. Response times may be
        longer during weekends and holidays. Thank you for your patience!
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .static-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
  }

  .contact-page h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #1a202c;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-page section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .contact-page h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #2d3748;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method {
    background: #f7fafc;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-method h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-method p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-detail a {
    color: #2b6cb0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-detail a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .faq-item {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
  }

  .faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #1a202c;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .response-time {
    background: #ebf8ff;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .response-time h2 {
    border-bottom: none;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .response-time p {
    color: #4a5568;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
